        <updateDate>2021-10-06T18:21:35Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Lowest Price for Patients Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires pharmacies to disclose to consumers when dispensing a prescription drug (1) the cost of the drug under the consumer's insurance plan, and (2) the cost of the drug without using their plan.</p>]]>
        </text>
